#: ../../P/pico-.rst:9
msgid ""
"[SI: a quantifier meaning × 10-12] Smaller than :ref:`nano-`\\; used in the "
"same rather loose connotative way as :ref:`nano-` and :ref:`micro-`\\. This "
"usage is not yet common in the way :ref:`nano-` and :ref:`micro-` are, but "
"should be instantly recognizable to any hacker. See also "
":ref:`quantifiers`\\, :ref:`micro-`\\."
msgstr ""
"[SI:× 10-12を意味する量詞]\\ :ref:`nano-`\\ より小さい。\\ :ref:`nano-`\\ や\\ "
":ref:`micro-`\\ と同じくかなり緩い含意的なやり方で使われる。この用法は\\ :ref:`nano-`\\ や\\ "
":ref:`micro-`\\ ほどまだ一般的ではないが、どんなハッカーにも即座に認識できるはずである。\\ :ref:`quantifiers`\\ "
"、\\ :ref:`micro-`\\ も参照。"
